headline: VMC Q4 Deep Dive: Data Center Demand and Project Timing Weigh on Margins
summary: Construction materials company Vulcan Materials (NYSE:VMC) missed Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q4 CY2025 as sales rose 3.2% year on year to $1.91 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.70 per share was 19.5% below analysts’ consensus estimates.
